titleInfo.title: Neitzke v. Husqvarna Professional Outdoor Products
titleInfo.subTitle: MEMORANDUM AND ORDER that plaintiff shall serve responses to defendant's outstanding discovery requests on or before December 15, 2006. Counsel shall confer and schedule the plaintiff's deposition on or before January 12, 2007. Counsel shall arrange to mediate this dispute as soon after January 12, 2007 as practicable, or alternatively report to the court the reasons why the case cannot be mediated to resolution. Another telephone conference with counsel shall be held at 11:00 a.m. February 7, 2007 for the purpose of further scheduling the matter to trial or other disposition. Ordered by Magistrate Judge David L. Piester. (CS, )
